---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Manifesto" description="Growth is not accidental. It is earned through sustained, deliberate effort.">
  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal noise-overlay topo-pattern py-24 md:py-36 px-6 md:px-12 pt-32 md:pt-40">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="scroll-reveal">
        <h1 class="font-display text-bone text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">
          Manifesto
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 1: dark -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal text-bone noise-overlay py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="scroll-reveal">
        <blockquote class="font-display font-light text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.1] tracking-wide mb-8 md:mb-12 text-bone">
          &ldquo;Growth is not accidental.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-reveal" data-delay="200">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-reading reading-width text-bone/70">
          It is the result of sustained, deliberate pressure applied over time. Not once. Not when convenient. Every day that the work asks you to show up, you show up.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: light -->
  <section class="bg-bone text-charcoal py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="scroll-reveal">
        <blockquote class="font-display font-light text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.1] tracking-wide mb-8 md:mb-12 text-charcoal">
          &ldquo;The present does the work. The future collects.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-reveal" data-delay="200">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-reading reading-width text-muted">
          Every repetition, every draft, every hard conversation, every early morning — these are deposits into an account you cannot yet see. Trust the arithmetic.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: dark -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal text-bone noise-overlay py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="scroll-reveal">
        <blockquote class="font-display font-light text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.1] tracking-wide mb-8 md:mb-12 text-bone">
          &ldquo;Comfort is a direction, not a destination.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-reveal" data-delay="200">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-reading reading-width text-bone/70">
          The pursuit of ease is a slow erosion. Not because comfort is wrong, but because it is incomplete. Character requires friction. It always has.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: light -->
  <section class="bg-bone text-charcoal py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="scroll-reveal">
        <blockquote class="font-display font-light text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.1] tracking-wide mb-8 md:mb-12 text-charcoal">
          &ldquo;We choose the hard path knowing the payoff is worth it.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-reveal" data-delay="200">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-reading reading-width text-muted">
          Not because suffering is virtuous. Not because difficulty proves anything on its own. But because the person who emerges from the work is someone you would want to be. Training, building, raising, creating, enduring — the domains change, but the principle does not.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: dark, no body, largest scale -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal text-bone noise-overlay py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="scroll-reveal">
        <blockquote class="font-display font-light text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-[1.1] tracking-wide text-bone">
          &ldquo;Thank yourself later.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Closing mark -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal noise-overlay py-20 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="scroll-reveal">
      <span class="font-display text-bone/30 text-sm tracking-mega-wide uppercase">
        Builds Character
      </span>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
